name: H&R Block Canada 2014 Tax Return
summary: Learn about .H14 files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: NOTE: H&R Block Canada tax return files reflect the year for which they contain tax data. The .H13 file contains tax return data for 2013 and .H12 contains tax data for 2012.

description: Tax return created and used by H&R Block Canada 2014, a Canadian tax preparation program; contains tax data entered by the user along with Canadian federal income tax forms; saves the progress of a tax return so it can be resumed at a later time.
